name: GeoAviR-examples
body: This page is a link to my github, providing example R scripts to use with our GeoAviR package. Also visit GeoAviRWeb.ddns.net for more info and to use our Shiny app to compute seabird at-sea densities from strip- or line-transect at-sea observations.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
